snippet.title: R.L Cantale
snippet.description: I am a mental health worker I live in the city of Los Angeles and very keen on  justice for men and women !  when it comes to abuse . I am here trying to shed some light on this dark mess . I do believe he's innocent I do believe Johnny is innocent as well . There's not enough women talking about the Manson cases so I will be reading and keeping  update with the accusations and the whole conspiracy . . I usually post  live because I like to hang out and look at the comments of you all but I promise I do more short upload soon. I had been reading the Manson accusations court filings since April. One by one so that takes times .So I hope that you find this interesting and informative . plz stick around so you can make this good !I could be all over the place and I'm not buying good equipment But not giving up ! .Please subscribe keep watching and share the truth. .
